title: The Angels' Buzz Bidstrup asks Australians to dig deep for Indigenous health
text:
Topix › Pacific Travel › The Angels' Buzz Bidstrup asks Austra... The Angels' Buzz Bidstrup asks Australians to dig deep for Indigenous health Next Story Prev Story 3 hrs ago Read more: The Age 
Graham `Buzz' Bidstrup has organised a concert as part of a crowd funding campaign to raise money for a charity that provides health programs for Indigenous people. When musician Jimmy Little was dying three years ago he made one wish to his mate and manager Graham "Buzz" Bidstrupa , asking him to continue running his namesake charity, the Jimmy Little Foundation.
